node.text: With a little imagination and some Little People friends (and some glue and cotton balls), you’ll be playing in a winter wonderland. Check out the festive fun from @5.min.crafts . ❄

node.title: DIY Ideas to Elevate Play Time with Little People and 5-Minute Crafts

node.text: Celebrating 90 years of play. And shapes and ABCs and rainbow rings and Little People and puppies and telephones with eyes and happy apples and BigFoot and singing sloths and let’s be kids! #FP90

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Fisher-Price on September 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'fp Fisher- Fisher-Price @FisherPrice Grandparents are like parents with less rules and more cookies. ©2021 MATTEL.'.

node.text: And we’re not talking ‘bout the raisin kind.
